

+----------------+----------------------------+-------------------------------+------------------------------------+
|   Feature        |  String                     | StringBuilder                 | StringBuffer                    |
+----------------+----------------------------+-------------------------------+------------------------------------+
| 1. Mutability     | Immutable                  | Mutable                       | Mutable                         |
+----------------+----------------------------+-------------------------------+------------------------------------+
| 2. Thread Safety  | Yes                        | No                            | Yes                             |
+----------------+----------------------------+-------------------------------+------------------------------------+
| 3. Performance    | Slow (due to immutability) | Fast (no synchronization)     | Slower (due to synchronization) |
+----------------+----------------------------+-------------------------------+------------------------------------+
| 4. Storage        | String pool (for literals) | Heap                          | Heap                            |
+----------------+----------------------------+-------------------------------+------------------------------------+
| 5. Use Case       | Small, fixed texts         | Single-threaded apps          | Multi-threaded apps             |
+----------------+----------------------------+-------------------------------+------------------------------------+
